column2: SELECT top # sp.ra,sp.dec,sp.z,sp.class,sp.subclass, so.class_noqso, so.subclass_noqso,so.class,so.subclass, so.spectroFlux_u, w.w1mpro AS w1, w.w2mpro AS w2, w.w3mpro AS w3, w.w4mpro AS w4, f.peak,f.integr,f.rms, sp.zwarning FROM SpecPhoto AS sp JOIN SpecObj AS so ON so.specObjID = sp.ObjID JOIN wise_xmatch AS xm ON sp.objid = xm.sdss_objid JOIN FIRST AS f ON sp.objid = f.objid JOIN wise_allsky AS w ON xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr WHERE (sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r > #)
